'''硫酮'''（英文：Thioketone）是[[酮|酮]]的[[氧|氧]]原子被[[硫|硫]]原子取代后形成的一类[[有机硫化合物|有机硫化合物]]，通式为R-C(=S)-R'，含有[[硫羰基|硫羰基]]（-C<sup>=S</sup>-）。

氧族元素中，由酮、硫酮再到[[硒酮|硒酮]]，稳定性显著下降。<ref name=Oka>{{cite journal | author = Okazaki, R.; Tokitoh, N. | title = Heavy Ketones, the Heavier Element Congeners of a Ketone | journal = [[Accounts_of_Chemical_Research|Accounts of Chemical Research]] | year = 2000 | volume = 33 | pages = 625–630 | doi = 10.1021/ar980073b}}</ref>大多数酮都是稳定的。而相比之下，位阻较小的硫酮大多不稳定，容易成环或生成[[聚合物|聚合物]]。例如，[[二苯甲酮|二苯甲酮]]是个稳定的白色固体；[[二苯甲硫酮|二苯甲硫酮]]是一个深蓝色较稳定的化合物，可溶于有机溶剂，露置于空气中时光解为[[二苯甲酮|二苯甲酮]]和硫；但再往下的二苯甲硒酮不稳定，可与1,3-二烯发生[[DA反应|DA反应]]，<ref>{{cite journal | author = Erker, G.; Hock, R.; Krüger, C.; Werner, S.; Klärner, F.-G. and Artschwager-Perl, U. | title = Synthesis and Cycloadditions of Monomeric Selenobenzophenone | journal = [[Angewandte_Chemie_International_Edition_in_English|Angewandte Chemie International Edition in English]] | year = 1990 | volume = 29 | pages = 1067–68 | doi = 10.1002/anie.199010671}}</ref>且会发生可逆性的聚合。

硫酮可通过[[酮|酮]]与[[劳氏试剂|劳氏试剂]]、[[氯化氢|氯化氢]]与[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]的混合物，或[[双(三甲硅基)硫化物|双(三甲硅基)硫化物]]反应引入硫原子得到。<ref>{{cite journal| title = Some Recent Synthetic Routes to Thioketones and Thioaldehydes"| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_chemical-society-great-britain-chemical-society-reviews_1993-06_22_3/page/199| author =W. M. McGregor, D. C. Sherrington| journal = [[Chemical_Society_Reviews|Chemical Society Reviews]] | volume = 22| pages = 199–204| year = 1993| doi = 10.1039/CS9932200199}}</ref>

